Class SpecialType

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.reinert.requestor.Payload
      • io.reinert.requestor.types.SpecialType
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ArrayBufferType, BlobType, DocumentType, JsonType

    public abstract class SpecialType
extends Payload
    Represents a javascript type that XMLHttpRequest handles without serialization. An SpecialType escapes the serialization when processing.
